# Single-owner repo: every PR auto-requests review from @1iamm.
# Even if branch protection doesn't *require* review (you're one person),
# this populates the "Reviewers" sidebar so you don't miss new PRs.
#
# Format: <path-pattern> @owner1 @owner2 ...
# Order matters — last matching pattern wins.

# Default catch-all.
* @1iamm

# CI / tooling — same owner, kept here for clarity if a future contributor
# joins and wants finer-grained ownership.
/.github/         @1iamm
/scripts/         @1iamm
/openspec/        @1iamm
